latestIgtvVideos.title: Everyday Makeup Routine I Quick & Easy Makeup Tutorial
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Makeup is my go-to option for every mood. Too bored? Create a new look. Too excited? Buy new makeup ? Too sad? Do a grunge-themed look. 🌚 You get the drift, riiiight? 👾

So, today I’m doing an everyday, light makeup look. And for the same, I’m using Blue Heaven’s BB cream (which provides a nice low to medium coverage), intense black kajal (smooth to apply and very blendable), eyeliner (a precise applicator gives a long lasting look), mascara (gives a nice, fanned out look to the eyelashes), and Barbie Doll Pink lipstick (used both as a lip colour and blusher). 💄💋

So, with just a few products, I’ve created a whole look that’s not only natural and light but it’s absolutely Instagram-worthy too. Which product would you like to try from Blue Heaven? Tell me in the comments. ♥️💯
